  itemIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 68d354cea1bb7e54e9a40bd7c95aebdb, type: 3}
  description: Increases Attack Speed by 10% and Ability Power by 10. Each basic
    attack grants a stack of "Flicker", increasing Attack Speed by an additional
    5%. This effect stacks infinitely until the end of the combat. A curved blade
    of exquisite elven craft that feels weightless in the hand; it moves with such
    supernatural celerity that it strikes before the wielder even consciously decides
    to swing.
